tag: How many [unit_count:hours] have passed since the [time_filter_exact1:exact-last] time patient {patient_id} was transferred to careunit {careunit} on the current hospital visit?

question: when was the last time on the last hospital visit that patient 18567931 was prescribed miconazole 2% cream.
template: when was the last time that patient 18567931 was prescribed miconazole 2% cream on the last hospital visit?
query: select prescriptions.starttime from prescriptions where prescriptions.hadm_id in ( select admissions.hadm_id from admissions where admissions.subject_id = 18567931 and admissions.dischtime is not null order by admissions.admittime desc limit 1 ) and prescriptions.drug = 'miconazole 2% cream' order by prescriptions.starttime desc limit 1
q_tag: when was the [time_filter_exact1] time that patient {patient_id} was prescribed {drug_name} [time_filter_global1]?
tag: When was the [time_filter_exact1:exact-last] time that patient {patient_id} was prescribed {drug_name} [time_filter_global1:rel-hosp-last]?

question: when did patient 17731115 last come out of hospital in 2105?
template: when was the last hospital discharge time of patient 17731115 in 2105?
query: select admissions.dischtime from admissions where admissions.subject_id = 17731115 and strftime('%y',admissions.admittime) = '2105' order by admissions.dischtime desc limit 1
q_tag: when was the [time_filter_exact1] hospital discharge time of patient {patient_id} [time_filter_global1]?
tag: When was the [time_filter_exact1:exact-last] hospital discharge time of patient {patient_id} [time_filter_global1:abs-year-in]?
